reviews.text:
The church is quite small but has a cozy and sacred atmosphere. I was especially impressed by the statues of Saints along the entrance to the church. It is simple in exterior, but the interior is beautiful. The time for mass is as below:

+ Weekday Mass (Monday - Friday):  6.30 AM & 6.30 PM;
+ Weekday Mass (Saturday): 6.30 AM;
+ Saturday Sunset Mass: 4.00 PM;
+ Sunday: 8.30AM & 11.00AM & 5.00PM.
